snippet.title: Pushpa 2 - The Rule Trailer (Hindi) | Allu Arjun | Sukumar | Rashmika Mandanna | Fahadh Faasil | DSP
snippet.description:
Wait Is Over, The Ruler Has Come🔥! Presenting "Pushpa 2 The Rule Trailer (Hindi)". 

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. The film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Navin Nooli respectively.

Releasing in Cinemas on 5th December 2024💥😍🔥!

Book your movie tickets on District ▶️ https://link.district.in/DSTRKT/Pushpa2TheRule

snippet.title: TURKEY FRY | Vaan Kozhi Varuval | Traditional Village Style Turkey Fry Recipe | Vaan Kozhi Uppu Kari
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook spicy turkey fry recipe using the traditional method. We cook village-style turkey recipe using fewer ingredients, mainly shallots, dried chili, cold-pressed gingelly oil, and more.

We call this recipe Vaan Kozhi Uppu Kari, Vaan Kozhi Varuval.

The taste is spicy.

snippet.title: Raj Thackeray Invites Kamiya Jani For A Heartwarming Maharashtrian Sunday Brunch | CurlyTales
snippet.description:
Join me for a special episode of Sunday Brunch as I step into the home of one of Maharashtra’s most loved politicians, Raj Thackeray, for an authentic Maharashtrian breakfast! Known for his no-nonsense attitude and fiery speeches, Raj Thackeray reveals a completely different side—chilled out, nostalgic, and full of laughter.

Over a delicious spread of Sabudana Khichdi, Tadpe Poha, Sabudana Vada, Seera, and Batata Thalipeeth, we dive into his personal life, school memories, and his deep bond with the legendary Bala Saheb Thackeray. He shares heartwarming stories about their relationship, his love for Maharashtrian culture, and even some hilarious anecdotes from his younger days.

This episode also features his son, Amit Thackeray, who is stepping into politics and gearing up for the electoral elections in Dadar and Mahim.

Watch as Raj Thackeray's "angry young man" persona takes a backseat to his warm and approachable vibe in this candid, fun-filled conversation. Don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe for more such unique stories and inspiring personalities!

06:30 - Memories With Bala Saheb

snippet.title: 👻 ভূতুড়ে রামের কাহিনী | Haunted Village Story | Wonder Munna #shorts #wondermunna
snippet.description:
Gopal was a young man living in Kolkata for work in the late 1800s. Every week, he would visit his village after finishing his work. But one time, because of extra work, he couldn’t go back for two weeks. When he finally returned to his village, something felt strange. Everything seemed different and a bit unsettling. As Gopal looked around, he couldn’t figure out why it all felt so wrong. What had changed in his absence?

#wondermunna #hauntedvillage

snippet.title: Paardarshi | Lashcurry | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
The first imagery of life that you see… is your home and your people. So today, I’m going to show you the things around my life… the things I’ve witnessed while growing from Vinayak to Lashcurry.

Song Credits

Track Name: Paardarshi
Written & Performed By: Lashcurry
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: Lashcurry
Track Name: Paardarshi
Singer/Performed By/Cast: Lashcurry
Lyricist/Written By: Lashcurry
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India


Follow Kaanphod to know more: 
👉 Subscribe to KaanPhod : https://www.youtube.com/@KaanPhodMusic 
👉 Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kaanphod 
👉 Follow us on X: https://x.com/kaanphodmusic?s=11 
👉 Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaanphodmusic/ 


Lyrics

Mein jaga jaga jaga Puri raat bhar 
Mein bhaga bhaga bhaga pichhe rakshas
Mein jana chahta waha jaha Shanti 
Gana gana gana gana lagta mujhe shrap ab

Kahani paardarshi sabhi ka istakbal
Kami kitabo ki par school gaya basta daal
Kabhi nahi aa paayi dawayi maa ki time par
Aaj maa ki ek khaasi pe Ghar bana aspataal

Khubiya chhod woh kamiya batake chale gayi
Samjha tha jindagi jindagi samjhakar chale gayi
Bola tha ek gaane pe ek peti utha lunga 
Woh kisi mahine Wale ki tamkhwa par chale gaye 

Na talasha mandiro mein  masjeedo mein 
khoya nahi 
Bandeesho mein hasta tha aur zanzeero mein
Roya nahi
Lanat hai uss bete par jo chori karke moz 
Karta
Baap jiska raat ko chain se kabhi soya nahi 

Naye makaano mein mandir purana yaad kar
Haath jod , aas kar , galtiyo ko maaf kar
Bada Dil , bada Ghar , lambi gehri saans bhar
Zubana mithi unke jinke khoon laga daat par

Bro , mein kehna chahta bhot kuchh 
Mata Peeta bhot khush 
Sannata dekha , roz dukh 
Ata nahi tha likhna ab likhta hoon baate bhot khoob 

Paayi paayi ke vaaste , bhai bhai mein  faasle
High figh si life ni si fi se haadse
Aight side mein but iya mice vice de haat mein
Lime light se door life line yeh art hai 

Baat suni mene Ghar ki chaar 
Toh darkinar ni Kari kalakari 
Padti maar jo jhadti maar ke 
Tapri paar the Farzi chaar 
Todke deeware dhar ki le gaye 
Thaane mein band hua agli baar
Baap ne bola aulad nahi meri 
Fir baap ne chhudaya apki baar 

Chalte show mein ata call 
papa bole kidhar ho
Jaldi aja Ghar pe mujhe 
Parwa nahi tum jidhar ho 
Ab mein jata show pe toh 
Utaar te hai Nazar pehle
Ab Mein chadta stage pe
Check pe 5 figure ho

Yeh saari cheeze ek raat mein ni aayi
Mein so Gaya bhula roti khairat mein nahi  khayi
Tu kalakar accha hai par mann mein tere khot
Warna accho acho ke safalta hath mein nahi ayi

Cheekhu zor se deeware mujhe khaa jayegi 
Chalta Jaa rha sadak pata nahi  kaha jayegi
Aaye din bas jaayedaat ke kagzat pe marpit 
Mein Ghar ka sabse Chhota mere hisse mein toh  maa aayegi

khoya nahi 
Bandeesho mein hasta tha aur zanzeero mein
Roya nahi

Aight side mein but iya mice vice de haat mein

papa bole kidhar ho

Chalta Jaa rha sadak pata nahi  kaha jayegi

snippet.title: 2nd ODI | Highlights | New Zealand Tour Of Sri Lanka | 17th November 2024
snippet.description:
In the second ODI, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Pallekele International Cricket Stadium. New Zealand batted first and posted 209 runs before getting all out in 45.1 overs. Sri Lanka showcased a great fighting spirit and chased down the target in 46 overs against a solid Kiwi bowling attack. In the end, Sri Lanka sealed a 3-wicket win and Kusal Mendis was the player of the match for his unbeaten 74-run knock.
.
.

snippet.title: পানবজাৰ  থানাৰ নিলম্বিত OC ভাৰ্গৱ বৰবৰাৰ বিপদ নিশ্চিত।
snippet.description: পানবজাৰ  থানাৰ নিলম্বিত OC ভাৰ্গৱ বৰবৰাৰ বিপদ নিশ্চিত। সমগ্ৰ ঘটনাক লৈ মুখ্যমন্ত্ৰীয়ে দিলে কঠোৰ বাৰ্তা। সৰ্বসাধাৰণৰ ওপৰত ক্ষমতাৰ অপপ্ৰয়োগ কোনো কাৰণতেই সহ্য কৰা নহয়। যদিহে জনতাক সন্মান কৰিব নাজানে তেন্তে এনে চাকৰি বাদ দিয়ক। অসম আৰক্ষীলৈ LOUD & CLEAR বাৰ্তা দিলে মুখ্যমন্ত্ৰী হিমন্ত বিশ্ব শৰ্মা

snippet.title: Stock market CRASH - SHOCKING बड़ा खेल | Ft. @VibhorVarshney  | Abhishek Kar Podcast
snippet.description:
Stock market CRASH - SHOCKING बड़ा खेल | Ft. Vibhor Varshney | Abhishek Kar Podcast
Indian Stock market has been falling badly since last few days and people are trying to identify the real reasons. While some are blaming the finance minster,others blame RBI and some to the continuous FII selling causing pain. In such a case what should investors do? Should they sell everything and sleep? Is recession going to come in? What to do with our mutual fund investments? Will state elections effect the market and lot more discussed with none other than SEBI Registered Research analyst @VibhorVarshney ! With his enormous experience of markets,he tells the real reason for the share market crash and the best solutions for the investors and traders. Don't forget to hit like and share for more such videos.
-
Time Stamps :
00:00:00 - Introduction
00:00:50 - What did you observe that made you believe the market would decline in the future?
00:02:57 - What is CPI (Consumer Price Index)?
00:05:20 - Do you think the market will fall like it did during the COVID-19 period?
00:07:07 - What changes have occurred in the US and India with Trump’s return?
00:08:58 - What advice would you give to the common people whose portfolios are down? Should they exit?
00:12:02 - Which category of stocks should one invest in?
00:15:20 - If I want to take risks for the long term, should I invest in small-cap stocks?
00:17:19 - Should we stop SIPs based on what influencers say?
00:23:00 - Vibhor Sir’s four favorite stock initials
00:26:40 - Should one buy physical gold or invest in gold?
00:30:42 - Conclusion and thank you

snippet.title: Buddy | Trailer | World Premiere | 16 November | 8PM | Hindi Dubbed | Colors Cineplex | Jio Cinema
snippet.description:
When Air Traffic Control officer Pallavi suffers a tragic accident, her soul enters a teddy bear, setting off a thrilling adventure. Teaming up with Aditya Ram, a daring pilot with a shared past, they embark on a high-stakes mission to Hong Kong to save her body from an organ-trafficking ring. *Buddy* is a gripping fantasy action film filled with emotion, suspense, and heart-pounding moments. Directed by Sam Anton and featuring Allu Sirish and Gayatri Bhardwaj, this is a story of love, courage, and second chances.

Teaming up with Aditya Ram, a daring pilot with a shared past, they embark on a high-stakes mission to Hong Kong to save her body from an organ-trafficking ring. *Buddy* is a gripping fantasy action film filled with emotion, suspense, and heart-pounding moments. Directed by Sam Anton and featuring Allu Sirish and Gayatri Bhardwaj, this is a story of love, courage, and second chances.

snippet.title: Big Breaking: India Emerges Front Runner to host Champions Trophy If Pak Pull Out  BCCI Reply Ready
snippet.description:
2025 ICC Champions Trophy : India to host champions trophy 2025 If Pakistan Pull Out  BCCI Reply Ready 
India is now the front runner to host the Champions Trophy 2025 if Pakistan pulls out to host the tournament in February 2025.
The ICC has asked the PCB for a response about hosting the Champions Trophy in a hybrid model after India refused to travel to Pakistan. The PCB confirmed on Sunday that it received an email from the ICC about India's decision.

The ICC has asked the PCB for a response about hosting the Champions Trophy in a hybrid model after India refused to travel to Pakistan. The PCB confirmed on Sunday that it received an email from the ICC about India's decision.

Aafat Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Abbas - Hibba Aziz - 17th November 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Warisha is a beautiful yet short-tempered girl living with her mother and stepfather. Warisha has followed the same misguided path that her mother, Mehak, took in the past. Influenced by her parents, Warisha has developed a greedy nature.

Wahaj, Warisha's paternal cousin, is a handsome young man in love with his cousin Shifa.However, neither Wahaj nor Shifa knows that Warisha is jealous of Wahaj and has bad intentions towards him and his family.

Will Warisha’s jealousy harm Wahaj’s love? Can Shifa and Wahaj marry with Warisha standing in their way? Will Warisha make a bad choice due to her parents’ influence? Will Wahaj and Shifa uncover Warisha’s real intentions?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Aafat Episode 36 - [Eng Sub] - Laiba Khan - Ali Abbas - Hibba Aziz - 17th November 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Warisha is a beautiful yet short-tempered girl living with her mother and stepfather. Warisha has followed the same misguided path that her mother, Mehak, took in the past. Influenced by her parents, Warisha has developed a greedy nature.

Wahaj, Warisha's paternal cousin, is a handsome young man in love with his cousin Shifa.However, neither Wahaj nor Shifa knows that Warisha is jealous of Wahaj and has bad intentions towards him and his family.

Will Warisha’s jealousy harm Wahaj’s love? Can Shifa and Wahaj marry with Warisha standing in their way? Will Warisha make a bad choice due to her parents’ influence? Will Wahaj and Shifa uncover Warisha’s real intentions?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

Episode 4243: Morning Chai
--------------------------------------------------------
The milk crisis hits Gokuldham Colony, leaving the residents chai-less. Later, Bhide finds himself torn between repairing his fridge or replacing it entirely.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4243 | 15 Nov 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Baal Baal Bache | 2 Foreigners In Bollywood
snippet.description:
https://Ka-adivasi.com +91-9980939672     91-9019225571   +91-9606899338 

Agency Partner - Influink.in
Heartwarming story of a grandmother’s love and a life-changing discovery.
Meet Prema Bua from Madhya Pradesh and her grandson Rohit, who has struggled with severe hair fall and gray hair, leading to a broken marriage and deep depression. After trying countless remedies to no avail, hope seemed lost… until his grandmother stepped in. Watch how their bond and her wisdom lead to an incredible transformation using Adivasi Hair Oil. A tale of resilience, family, and the power of age-old solutions.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Blesso Cosmetics

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.
